Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.61,0:06:19.06,OP-Kara2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,300)}Steppin' out to a dull morning
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.06,0:06:21.40,OP-Kara2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,300)}Wishin' for peace to my Bros & family
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:23.82,OP-Kara2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,300)}It may be hard, so I turn my heart on
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:26.02,OP-Kara2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,300)}Nothing'll put me down, fear's just an illusion
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.02,0:06:28.16,OP-Kara,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,300)}Who brought you here to face the future, girl
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.17,0:06:30.98,OP-Kara,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,300)}Guess what you've got to break, when the past calls
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.98,0:06:36.94,OP-Kara,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,300)}Digging every single sorrow up to burn 'em all away
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.94,0:06:39.01,OP-Kara3,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,300)}Be somebody who handles pain
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.01,0:06:41.94,OP-Kara3,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,300)}Isolate yourself Kandžiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.94,0:06:46.13,OP-Kara3,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,300)}Kawari Hadžimete juku Make your vibes
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.13,0:06:47.72,OP-Kara2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,300)}Show me your action
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:49.80,OP-Kara2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,300)}Give me ovation
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.81,0:06:51.60,OP-Kara2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,300)}It's time to move your body
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.60,0:06:52.57,OP-Kara2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,300)}You don't gotta be shy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.57,0:06:53.89,OP-Kara2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,300)}You only gotta aim high
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.88,0:06:55.93,OP-Kara2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,300)}We togetha now, don't gotta worry
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:06:56.61,OP-Kara3,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,300)}Don't give a damn
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.61,0:06:58.25,OP-Kara3,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,300)}Look, you’re standing here still
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.25,0:07:00.94,OP-Kara3,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,300)}Kicking the ground to get higher
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.93,0:07:03.14,OP-Kara,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,300)}Don't miss the beating of your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.14,0:07:05.48,OP-Kara,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,300)}Take a chance on you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:15.06,OP-Kara,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,300)}Te wo nobašite Hikari ni kaete
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.49,0:07:10.24,OP-Kara2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,300)}Reach out YOUR SOUL Your life's YOUR OWN
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.09,0:07:15.08,OP-Kara2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,300)}Changin' the lights to brighten your goal
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.08,0:07:19.90,OP-Kara,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,300)}No one could reach them No one but you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.77,0:07:19.91,OP-Kara2,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,300)}Only you can defeat the weaker you and achieve your dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.91,0:07:23.74,OP-Kara,,0,0,0,,{\fade(100,300)}Time to write a new story
